				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gia-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-S%E1%BB%9F-T%C3%A0i/%C3%82m-S%C6%A1n/poem-ca72WAW3cFoS47O8w34xaw">Âm Sơn - 陰山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gia-Lu%E1%BA%ADt-S%E1%BB%9F-T%C3%A0i/author-hW5UqHVoDIes9sj7tB65qg">Gia Luật Sở Tài</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Quy%E1%BB%83n/D%C3%A3-v%E1%BB%8Dng/poem-M3E8SYdKczNMru0BmISV0Q">Dã vọng - 野望</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Quy%E1%BB%83n/author-4t54z4Xp1Ge7tbVqJgjhQQ">Ông Quyển</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/Nam-H%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AB-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-KCUlPoYYLK793hIq4LIDng">Nam Hải từ vịnh kỳ 2 - 南海祠詠其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/author-raZnRizzmxsn-rfcNRwVcQ">Thích Đại Sán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%C3%B3ng-thuy%E1%BB%81n-T%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A1ch-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%C3%AA-huy%E1%BB%87n/poem-NEB-pU40M9FIVCdT1DUKtg">Phóng thuyền (Tống khách Thương Khê huyện) - 放船（送客蒼溪縣）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C3%A1i-du-Tam-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-s%C6%A1n/poem-Wki6pPRclrS2pgLCHua9xQ">Tái du Tam Điệp sơn - 再踰三疊山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-T%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%C3%AAn/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-T%C3%B4ng/poem-aSu9Zt-LcJmZ-cr9sCfnzw">Thạch Tông - 石淙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B5-T%E1%BA%AFc-Thi%C3%AAn/author-cFPknskEldD7UcWhT6LIfQ">Võ Tắc Thiên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BB%B3-l%C3%A3o-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-nCBvIN8amwPAFH9naL5zdQ">Thuỳ lão biệt - 垂老別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-V%C4%83n-Kh%C3%A2m/V%C3%A3n-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-Tr%C3%AD-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/poem-DRc4pRKEh4HCYCKZ8JHKvA">Vãn Quảng Trí thiền sư - 挽廣智禪師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-V%C4%83n-Kh%C3%A2m/author-60xEy6Le_KpaX7OUkThtVg">Đoàn Văn Khâm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Vi%E1%BB%85n-s%C6%A1n/poem-k7YjzOpB-lTBMIMS0M6qfA">Viễn sơn - 遠山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/V%C5%A9-h%E1%BA%ADu-kh%C3%A1n-s%C6%A1n/poem-kHVi31E29_19w8t-5bzYeg">Vũ hậu khán sơn - 雨後看山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/author-D3wrKcf7SBsjhsqBdwn9aw">Phan Đức Dư</a>)<br></div>	</div>
